node.text:
Werbung/Advertisement We cooked several dishes with the delicious products from @reishunger - which is one of the nominees for the German @amazon Verkaufspartner Awards, where all German and Austrian @amazon customers can vote for their favorite nominee and have the chance to get one of 100 vouchers each worth 100€. Find the link in our profile.
As you probably can guess @reishunger is selling all kinds of rice products. From black rice to rice-peas noodles and to rice pudding spices they offer a fantastic range with a fresh modern look and we really love the quality and taste. Check out our latest blog post for a little interview with @reishunger founders and get the recipes for all 3 dishes from the video.
#verkaufspartnerawards

node.title: Kale-rice salad, rice pasta with lentils and pink rice pudding

node.text:
Werbung|Advertisement We are so excited to team up with @kolonnenull a non-alcoholic premium wine brand from Germany. All their wines are vegan and contain a maximum of 0,3% residual alcohol content. We tested the Rosé Sparkling 2020 and the Burgundy Cuvée 2020 and loved them both! The Rosé Sparkling has a gentle balance - slightly sweet with a lively acidity and was the perfect match with our gluten-free chocolate-cherry cake and a wonderful refreshment during these hot summer days. You can buy all the wines in their own online shop, the link is in our profile and in stories. Cheers! 🍷✨ #kolonnenull 
___
#magicalmoments #momentslikethese #summermoments #gatheringslikethese #gathering #nonalcoholic #wineglass #tablesetting #tabledecor #tablestyling #foodstylist #foodphotographer

The cocktail is called Belvedere Air and is made with Belvedere Heritage 176, honey, almond milk, lemon juice and mint, perfect for a cozy summer evening 🌿☀️Get both recipes on the blog, link is in profile. #EnjoyResponsibly #BelvedereVodka #MadeWithNatur
